<hr /><h2 id="home-why-help"class="text-center">Why Help?</h2>
<div id="home-why-help-row" class="row">
    <h4 id="home-help-text" class="col-sm-8 text-center">The Cars That Care Foundation transforms donated vehicles into reliable transportation for struggling and deserving individuals.
When you donate money or your old vehicle, you are changing someone's life. Everyone deserves the chance to achieve independence and the ability to provide for their families. </h4>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4 home-step">
